file_content.text: Hang on. Emergency pod's almost secure, but not quite.
You're... with the Republic, aren't you?
That's right. I'm also saving your lives. You got a problem with that?
As a matter of fact, I do.
Yes.
Figured. Guess we'll have a chat about that when you get to the surface.
Just get us out of here.
I don't care.
Yeah, that's what I'm trying to do.
Hurry! I wasn't built to survive the crushing depths!
Wookiees are not built that way, either!
Okay, all set. Climb in and enjoy the ride.
Apologies, but the remote docking procedure isn't quite finished....
You're a Sith.
But not your enemy. Not today.
Now, are you still interested in a ride back, or would you prefer to swim?
Sith or not, I won't turn down a helping hand.
Let's go.
I do appreciate a pragmatic mind.
And I appreciate staying alive--let's go!
I'm not in the habit of trusting Sith.
I don't like this.
This seems like an excellent time to start.
A Sith can be fought--the ocean can't. Let's go!
...and there we are. Your transportation is ready--safe travels.
